ZH: 不论你是谁，我都会帮助你。
EN: No matter who you are, I will help you.

ZH: 不论外面的天气如何，我都会去跑步。
EN: Regardless of the weather outside, I will go for a run.

ZH: 不论你怎么说，我都不会改变主意。
EN: No matter how you say it, I will not change my mind.

ZH: 不论发生什么事情，我们都会一起面对。
EN: Whatever happens, we will face it together.

ZH: 不论他犯了什么错误，我都会原谅他。
EN: Regardless of his mistakes, I will forgive him.

ZH: 不论你选择哪个方向，我都会支持你。
EN: Whichever direction you choose, I will support you.

ZH: 不论你的选择是什么，我都尊重。
EN: Whatever your choice is, I will respect it.

ZH: 不论今天你觉得怎么样，明天会更好。
EN: Regardless of how you feel today, tomorrow will be better.

ZH: 不论障碍多大，我们都要坚持下去。
EN: No matter how big the obstacles are, we must persevere.

ZH: 不论多么困难，我们都要一起努力。
EN: Regardless of how difficult it is, we must work together.

ZH: 不论你想要什么，我都会尽力实现。
EN: Whatever you want, I will do my best to make it happen.

ZH: 不论结果如何，我都会感激你的帮助。
EN: Regardless of the outcome, I will be grateful for your help.

ZH: 不论你在哪里，我都会找到你。
EN: Wherever you are, I will find you.

ZH: 不论时间多久，我都会等你。
EN: No matter how long it takes, I will wait for you.

ZH: 不论他走到哪里，我都会跟在他后面。
EN: Wherever he goes, I will follow him.

ZH: 不论别人怎么想，我只在乎你的看法。
EN: Regardless of what others think, I only care about your opinion.

ZH: 不论风雨，我都会守护你。
EN: Come rain or shine, I will protect you.

ZH: 不论困难多大，我们都会战胜它。
EN: No matter how great the difficulty is, we will overcome it.

ZH: 不论成败，我们都要一起努力。
EN: Regardless of success or failure, we must work together.
